  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this prospective observational study, the investigators tried assess the presence of
      biofilm on chronic wound samples coming from a large cohort study of patients, whilst
      cross-referencing the clinical, bacteriological and wound care observations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
